INKCAZELO:

Iwebsite yase-Elsenburg iqulethe uluhlu oluhlaziyiweyo lwemicimbi yezolimo eya kube ibanjelwe apha kwiNtshona Kapa.


IMIYALELO:

Ukuze ube nokujonga le micimbi isezayo, tyelela apha www.elseburg.com

Kanti usenokufikelela nakuluhlu lwemicimbi esele idlulile.
Ukuba kunomcimbi wezolimo onokuthanda ufakwe kuluhlu olukule website, ungazingenisa iinkcukcha zaloo mcimbi ngokuthi usebenzise iphetshana elikule website lokungenisa imicimbi ekumila kunjalo.
